9	## 2. Purpose
10	
11	Log daily weight, view progress chart, and read stage-specific nutrition tips. This screen provides a personal weight tracking hub for health-conscious mothers, allowing users to monitor weight trends over time and receive pregnancy-stage-appropriate nutritional guidance based on their current pregnancy week.
12	
13	**Context:** Standalone push route from Browse tab. No bottom navigation visible on this screen. Primary interaction is adding new weight entries via FAB.
